{"tid":1507508,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"智慧監控燈柱的末日，壽終正寢，我心更興奮","createTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T10:44:45.000Z","uid":285345,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"caa62a31755c2410b6c8e8ca75aa2157c0b83dd5","tid":1507508,"uid":285345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1476873_1_20190826143043.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1476873_1_20190826143043.jpg&h=eaa4eee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n智慧燈柱供應商因員工安全受威脅停合作 創科局表遺憾<br />\n<br />\n在剛過去星期六觀塘區遊行期間，有示威者破壞九龍灣的智慧燈柱，質疑當局用以監控市民。<br />\n<br />\n智慧燈柱藍牙發射器供應商「訊科系統有限公司」在公司網頁發公告，表示基於公司董事的家人及僱員受到人身安全威脅，以及公眾對公司的項目和服務有疑慮，決定完成支援現時已安裝的50支燈柱的相關工作後，停止供應及安裝當局的智慧燈柱項目中其他智能裝置。希望能平息市民及客户的疑慮，並集中改善內部網絡安全及管理。<br />\n<br />\n創新及科技局發言人表示，同情理解，並尊重該公司的決定。發言人說，對於有本地中小企，因參與智慧燈柱項目而受到攻擊起底，表示難以接受，亦深表遺憾，形容事件嚴重打擊香港創科界的努力。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476873-20190826.htm?fbclid=IwAR2IGo-a552NL2N0IpLU-uUjvU-B1bunzF75qGFERvRpfk08flb48TcWh2E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476873-20190826.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2IGo-a552NL2N0IpLU-uUjvU-B1bunzF75qGFERvRpfk08flb48TcWh2E&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY6xOsK%2BJamotDVaNSe1I1zI%3D&h=c98dd582\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476873-20190826.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2IGo-a552NL2N0IpLU-uUjvU-B1bunzF75qGFERvRpfk08flb48TcWh2E&h=62fce964\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476873-20190826.htm?fbclid=IwAR2IGo-a552NL2N0IpLU-uUjvU-B1bunzF75qGFERvRpfk08flb48TcWh2E</a>"},{"pid":"095e5a581422c46e1775a97509717b3f5be17e82","tid":1507508,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" da